#### Report Generation Template

```markdown
# Activity Report: [Author Name] - [Date Range]

## Summary

- **Period**: [Start Date] to [End Date]
- **Total Commits**: [X] commits
- **Files Changed**: [X] files
- **Lines Added**: +[X]
- **Lines Removed**: -[X]
- **Primary Focus**: [Main feature/area worked on]

## Features Implemented

### [Feature Name]

